title: 155: Super Bowl LI preview
itunes:title: 155: Super Bowl LI preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the matchups to watch for in Super Bowl LI. The Atlanta Falcons led the NFL in scoring this season, so how does the Patriots defense stop them? What can the Falcons defense do to stop Tom Brady's attempt for a fifth ring. DJ and Bucky also reveal their picks for the biggest game of the year.
